Pyhton look for modules in the following order:
    local directory
    Lib
    site-packages

Python's lib directory is for standard packages

To use your a module you created from any directory place module in site-packages
usr/local/lib/pythonx.y/site-packages


import example --> import some_module
usage          --> some_module.some_function()

import example --> from some_module import some_function
usage          --> some_function()

import example --> from some_module import some_function as f
usage          --> f()